parameters: Would you like to move to the reminiscence room?
It's possible to carry \ii[253] with \ii[252]. What will you do?
\ii[253] has been added to the 'Important Items' in your inventory.

From now on, by using the item \ii[253], you can move to the
reminiscence room anytime, from anywhere.
Liese seems oddly happy about it.

Liese: "It's okay, you can come in~ Shall we take a shower
together...?"
Flora: "No, I'm fine. And I'm not a pervert..."
Liese: "I feel so refreshed~ Thanks for letting me go first~"
Flora: "Well then, I guess it's my turn to take a shower."
Flora: "Wow, there's even a bed! What a lovely room~"

In many towns and villages, there are inns where you can recover HP
and MP by sleeping in a bed. Some accommodations, like this inn, are
fully equipped with showers and toilets.

Additionally, each inn has a book of recollections, allowing you to
move to the recollection room. After obtaining the Book Holder, you
can carry it with you.

You can check the help and set the difficulty level from the
'Adventure Log' and 'Options' in the menu, respectively.

Will you rest in the bed?
Flora and Liese can now use Combo Attack 1!

As their intimacy level increases, they can perform stronger combo
attacks. Be aware that after using a combo attack, it cannot be used
again for several turns.

Additionally, intimacy levels can be raised by sleeping together and
other forms of physical contact. (Please refer to the Adventure Book's
help section for more details.)
